Title: Null and Void
Description:
We must defeat that loathsome apparition of Turalyon.

The abomination's presence is intolerable. If left unchecked, it may destroy what remains of Telogrus Rift. 

I will end it with my own hands.
ObjectivesText: Defeat the Corrupted Memory of Turalyon in Telogrus Rift.
PortraitGiverText: A manifestation of Alleria's worst nightmare, conjured by the Harbinger.
